Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I go to Page 02 of Hip MRI

Then 'Endoprosthesis' checkbox is enabled
And 'Labral surgery' checkbox is enabled
And 'Offset correction' checkbox is enabled
And 'Cartilage transplantation' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Endoprosthesis' checkbox
Then 'Right' checkbox is enabled
And 'Left' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Labral surgery' checkbox
Then 'Right' checkbox is enabled
And 'Left' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Offset correction' checkbox
Then 'Right' checkbox is enabled
And 'Left' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Cartilage transplantation' checkbox
Then 'Autologous matrix-induced chondrogenesis (AMIC)' radio button is enabled
And 'Autologous chondrocyte transplantation (ACT)' radio button is enabled 
And 'Right' checkbox is enabled
And 'Left' checkbox is enabled
